<section id="about-us">
    <h2>About HacktoberWall</h2>
    <p>HacktoberWall is an initiative designed to celebrate open-source contributions during Hacktoberfest. It serves as a platform where developers can showcase their projects, connect with the community, and inspire others to participate in open-source development.</p>
    <h3>Owners</h3>
    <div class="owners">
        <div class="owner">
            <img id="jolly-profile" alt="Jolly's GitHub Profile Picture" />
            <h4>Jolly (Owner)</h4>
            <p>A passionate open-source advocate with years of experience in software development. Jolly is committed to fostering a collaborative environment in the tech community.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="owner">
            <img id="phanty-profile" alt="Phanty78's GitHub Profile Picture" />
            <h4>Phanty78 (Co-Owner)</h4>
            <p>A creative developer and designer who loves working on community-driven projects. Phanty78 aims to make technology accessible and enjoyable for everyone.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
